author: Washington Free Beacon Staff
title: Hillary Clinton Accidentally Retweets Late Night Comedy Host Mocking Trump
text:
Former Democratic 2016 presidential nominee Hillary Clinton retweeted and then deleted a photo posted by the "Full Frontal with Samantha Bee" Twitter account that was making fun of the lack of women in President Donald Trump's White House administration on Wednesday.
The "Full Frontal with Samantha Bee" Twitter account tweeted a picture of Trump in the Oval Office with health insurance CEO's from late February, the Washington Examiner reported .
The original Tweet from "Full Frontal" said, "The Trump WH is so feminist, EVERY day is Day Without a Woman."
This was retweeted—and then deleted—by Hillary Clinton. pic.twitter.com/WaTvAMP4IC 
— Kyle Griffin (@kylegriffin1) March 8, 2017 
Multiple journalists screen-grabbed the image of Hillary Clinton retweeting the TBS TV show's account.
"Full Frontal with Samantha Bee" is a political comedy show on TBS.
The post Hillary Clinton Accidentally Retweets Late Night Comedy Host Mocking Trump appeared first on Washington Free Beacon .
